==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-sock.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɒk|-ɒk]]

===Noun===
'''sock''' ('''socks''' ''or'' '''sox''')
# a knitted or woven covering for the foot
# a shoe worn by Greco-Roman comedy actors
# a violent blow, punch

====Related terms====
*[[sock puppet]]
*[[bobby sock]]

